block.p: DILNO--Dennis. February 18, 1946 -January 27, 2007. Beloved partner of Jeff Glenn, Chicago. Brother of Jeri Dilno and Sandy Millender, California. Uncle to Roy III and Don Millender. Friend to many at Simpson Thacher & Price Waterhouse. Gathering and service 12-3 pm, February 3, at Greenwich Village Funeral Home, Bleecker and 6th Ave., NYC. Donations to Lambda Legal or NY LGBT Center.
